**5. Complete Pipeline Flow**

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| **Full Automation: Trend to Published Video**                         |
|                                                                       |
| E1 (7 AM) → Discovers 7-15 wellness trends from RSS + Reddit + PubMed |
|                                                                       |
| QUANTUM (8 AM) → Selects top trends, creates 6 briefs, sends to       |
| Telegram                                                              |
|                                                                       |
| HUMAN → Approves/Rejects briefs on Telegram                           |
|                                                                       |
| E2 (auto) → Generates scripts, captions, storyboards + 3-gate QA      |
|                                                                       |
| HUMAN → Reviews content, presses Publish                              |
|                                                                       |
| E3 (auto) → Generates video, adds branding, runs Technical QA         |
|                                                                       |
| HUMAN → Reviews video preview, confirms Final Publish                 |
|                                                                       |
| E3 (auto) → Schedules post via Buffer, logs everything to PostgreSQL  |
|                                                                       |
| Human touchpoints: 3 (Brief approval, Content publish, Video confirm) |
|                                                                       |
| Automated steps: Everything else                                      |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

