**6.2 Docker Stack Addition**

FFmpeg will be added to the n8n Docker container for video
post-processing (subtitle burning, branding overlay, format conversion).
No new container needed.

Video files will be stored temporarily in a shared Docker volume between
n8n and a new R2/S3-compatible storage bucket for asset management. For
MVP, local file storage within the Docker volume is sufficient.

